messages.content: Wanderer’s mindscape looks like a futuristic seaside town made almost entirely of candy and cakes.
Suddenly, the landscape seemed to darken and the vibes got...scary...
“Huh?!” Wanderer looked up, shivering a bit.
There was a girl wandering around clearly confused "H-How did I get here...."
"Uh....is this your mindscape? Im so sorry if Ive ruined it..."
“How did you get in here anyway?”
She shook her head "I never get much sleep..."
"Its alright ive learned to deal with it.."
".....Your....young. Oh god I should leave. I dont wanna give you nightmares..."
Wanderer is joined by a shadowy monster in a blue dress.
The shadow monster changed into a human female.
It looked down at her with concern in its eyes, but she shook her head.
The kid stumbled into the mindscape, looking around to get a better view of his surroundings

Wanderer followed behind him. It looked like a futuristic island town, with a few scattered carnival rides. One island even had a city that seemed like a mix of both her style and 1920s.
There was another shadowy figure, this one wearing a blue spotted dress.
He gulped and scrambled behind Wanderer, shaking a little when seeing the figure

The figure tilted her head, looking confused as to why he was scared. 
“D-Dont worry, he‘s just...nervous around newcomers!” She said quickly.
He still shaking, though he feels as though another presence behind him, one that was staring daggers at the Suzi Q shadow. “H-Huh...?”

Suzi tilted her head, approaching the other presence. 
Wanderer heard him and turned around, before gasping in surprise. “Woah!”
Shadow Veteris leaps in front of Iuvenis, assuming a offense form, wary of the approaching shadow
Suzi looks genuinely scared. “L-Like I said, she’s nice...” wanderer said softly.

They calm down a bit, dropping the form, though still not moving away from Iuvenis.
The boy turns and shakes his head at the shadow, they now having an apologetic expression in his eyes

“It’s all right, I understand...” she said quietly. 
The female monster seems very interested in Verteris.

“W-Well...th-this is...aw-awkward..” 
Vet, takes a step towards The monster, his head cocked to the side,unsure of what to do

“A-A little...I didn’t expect him to follow us.”
She waved cautiously at him.

The waved back awkwardly, blinking in confusion,
“A-At least...th-they’re not...f-fighting...?”

“T-True...” she nodded. 
She tilted her head, looking at his outfit.
He looked away...in embarrassment...?  It’s really hard to tell what he’s feeling ~~just like the real thin~~
Apparently he didn’t think his clothes he was created with were suiting compared to hers
She looked concerned, gesturing at her dress.
He shakes his head and gestures at his own clothes, looking disappointed
“...” She claps her hands together in understanding and a little bit of shame.
He panicky waves hands, not wanting her to be ashamed, points at her dress and does a heart sign with his hands
Her expression brightens and she jumps up and down, excited.
However, you could faintly hear an anguished cry on an island, something like “Caesar!”?
He looks around, looking a little disturbed by the yell,

Suzy looked saddened. 
“Don’t worry about it, it...actually happens quite often.”

Seteris puts a hand on her shoulder comfortingly 
“S-So somemun is a-always yelling ce-CEASAR?”
“N-No, not always...its more like every few days.”
She nodded. “B-But it does keep the monsters away from me, so...it’s something.”
Veteris squeezed her shoulder in reassurance
She looked oddly surprised at his touch.
He shyly looks down, tapping his feet,
Suzy glanced down at his feet.
It’s seems his other hand is outstretched to hers
He softly grips it and gives a quiet humming noise. Looking very pleased.
She hums back, smiling a bit.

“H-Huh....I guess t-t-that’s a....*good* t-thing?”
V’s cold demeanor was now completely off, now just a awkward idiot.

“Y-Yeah, but...she’s never been like this with anyone who isn’t me before.”
Suzy purred at him- her tail would be wagging if she had one.

_________
Aion is terrified of the goop.
:) whats this? Theres a very tiny amount of goop. Trying to make itself look friendly by coping Dulcis shape
"We dont want to hurt you little ome...." she kneels down "Ill keep my distance but if you let us go your sister will still be safe..."

“Y-You promise...?” She asked. 
Suzy Q watched over this, but she looked...different, somehow.
She nodded, opening her arms for a hug if the other wanted it
She looked cautious, before slowly hugging her.
She gently hugged back, patting the others head.
She whimpered quietly. “...Will you...leave her alone?”
"Dear her body is so good....all we want is to have a body....We dont want to be kept in a cage anymore...."
“B-But there’s plenty of bodies you could use! You could be a bird, or a cat, or a bear! There’s so many things you could be, so why my sister?”
"We want a body that can allow us to blend into every day life....We want to feel things, we want to do things."
“...” She looked saddened. The goop had a point.
"We have been locked up for so long...we are sentient..."
“W-Well, Yeah, if you’re talking to me...”
"We have yearned for a body to call our own! And now we have many! And all are such wonderful bodys! Strong, talented, beautiful.  What more could we ask for?"
“...A single body, an identity that you can call *yours*.•
"Well yes, thats the ideal kind of body."
“You can’t really do that if you have all these other bodies, can you?”
"No...Not really. But it is better then nothing for now."
Her form was wavering "Gh- Th-The hamon....is hurting...."
Its form breaks and its gone silent
It shakes a little before recovering her form again
“B-But papa and I hurt you when you just wanted to live! That’s...that’s not very nice of us...”
"Little Aion....its ok...we promise..." It smiled a bit
She still looks unsure...and a bit surprised. “How did you know...?”
“Oh...” she nodded. “I-Is it OK if father comes in?”
It thought for a bit before nodding
He waves at aion and the goop.
She gestured at the goop. “This is, um.... do you *have* a name?”
It shook its head "No...we call ourselves the goop...."
"yes, I was. When I saw that my daughter being taken over, my anger blinded me, and I attacked you."
"...We....are sorry about that....If....it makes you feel better Dulci and Rodo are getting ice cream right now...."
“...Hey, have you ever thought about what you’d *want* to look like?”
"That is a fair question. Perhaps you could show it to us."
"....No....Not really....We really like how the females look though...."
“So you...think you’re a girl?” Aion smiles a bit.
“Hey, if you’re not sure, that’s fine! I flip flop between boy and girl sometimes! And sometimes I’m both!”
She smiled at that "Really??? You can...do that????"
“It’s pretty cool, isn’t it?” She grinned.
“A lot of Muns don’t fully conform to male or female, you’ll fit in great!”
"Aion gave you one earlier. It's a friendly embrace."
She thought for a bit before nodding
She smiled and hugged back. "We....we like hugs....they feel nice....."
"Thank you.....We do not wish to harm others....." She smiled
“We won’t hurt you anymore, well help you.”
“My stand let’s me make copies of myself. Maybe you could use one until we find a way to get you one all your own!”
“I know it’s not exactly *yours*, but it’s a start, right?”
A second, somewhat shadowy Aion joins the mindscape. “It’s all yours!”
The goop took over the second Aion
“There you go...wanna wake up and try it out?”
Aion finds herself back in her mindscape, twice over.
(What if there's a ball in here too)
They notice the goop and crouch down in front of them.

“Um...hello, Goop...”
The clone starts humming as well, trying to match their song.
“Th-That’s a pretty song... what is it?”
“I didn’t know you knew how to sing...or hum at least...”
“Radium...she’s the one making your new body, right?”

“Oh...”
“Maybe when we meet her, she can teach me a few of her songs...”
“Oh, they did?” She looked a little surprised. Polaris was in on this?!
She purred happily, wagging her tail.
Aion was trembling in her mindscape.
Momo sees this and hugs her
“O-Oh, yeah...th-then why did you use Meriad?”
She giggled a bit, hugging her.
“A-And I think this is a big fight...”
She nodded. “A fight to free us all...”
She hugged her again. “I’m...glad you’re here.”
She hugged her "Im glad to be able to see you...."
After a little bit, she’s back in her mindscape, shaking again.
“Dominus is mad... not at me, hopefully, but...”
"Oh no....Ill get Meriad to head to the temple...."
“N-No, I don’t think it’s because Meriad isn’t here... two of the kids here were hurt somehow...”
